{sow_summary}

Service Line Design Standards:
{standards_context}

HLD Context (use HLD integration points as starting point — add field-level detail):
{hld_context}

Generated Requirements Context:
{requirements_context}

REMINDER: Each bidirectional integration = ONE section with a Direction column in the mapping table.
Two separate sections for the same integration pair = WRONG.
"Map to corresponding status" without showing actual values = WRONG.
Trigger must be a specific event (Platform Event / Business Rule / Scheduled job) — not a lifecycle description.

Now generate the Integration Mapping for {project_name}. All system names and field names from THIS project's context. Do NOT add a "Note:" section. Output ONLY markdown.
